  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_hire_main</Cell><Cell>I want to hire some mercenaries.</Cell><Cell>Chci najmout nějaké žoldáky.</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_hire_main</Cell><Cell>There are some lads that are willing to help. How strong should they be?</Cell><Cell>Je tu pár chlapů, co rádi pomůžou. Jak silní by měli být?</Cell></Row>
  
  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_weak</Cell><Cell>The weakest will do.</Cell><Cell>Ti nejslabší budou stačit.</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_weak</Cell><Cell>Alright, 50 groschen a head. How many do you need?</Cell><Cell>Dobrá, 50 grošů za hlavu. Kolik jich potřebuješ?</Cell></Row>
  
  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_medium</Cell><Cell>Some decent lads.</Cell><Cell>Nějaké slušné chlapy.</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_medium</Cell><Cell>Alright, 100 groschen a head. How many do you need?</Cell><Cell>Dobrá, 100 grošů za hlavu. Kolik jich potřebuješ?</Cell></Row>
  
  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_good</Cell><Cell>An experienced Soldier.</Cell><Cell>Zkušené vojáky.</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_good</Cell><Cell>Top quality. That's 300 groschen a head. How many do you need?</Cell><Cell>Prvotřídní kvalita. To je 300 grošů za hlavu. Kolik jich potřebuješ?</Cell></Row>
  
  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_count_1</Cell><Cell>Just one.</Cell><Cell>Jen jednoho.</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_count_2</Cell><Cell>I'll take two.</Cell><Cell>Vezmu si dva.</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_count_3</Cell><Cell>Give me three of them.</Cell><Cell>Dej mi jich tři.</Cell></Row>

